(SYSOP限定, option _AUTOFWD in config.h)
The autorouter is only used for S&F, if no route is found in "fwd.bcm".

"afwdlist"            creates the file "afwd.bcm" if "autofwdtime" is not 0.
"autofwdtime 0"       disables the autorouter.
