構文: CLOG ["<検索文字列>"]

Shows last 2 kBytes of file "trace/cmdlog.bcm". All sysop commands are logged
here. If you add <search string> all lines where this string is found will be
shown. You only need " " if <search string> should contain spaces. You can use
as <search string> also date or time string. The <search string> is handled as
regular expression.

See also HELP REGULAR_EXPRESSIONS
