\\FLEXNET.WRITE
(SYSOP限定)

WRITE <Flex-File>

Writes a textfile to harddisk. Input can be saved with ^Z or /EX.

<Flex-File> = A, B, C, H, I, L, S

The file will be saved in flexnet directory as e.g. "a.fpr". It's better to
send those files via BCM with WT or WPRG command.

