(SYSOP限定, init.bcm)
構文: UNSECURETTYPW [ 0 | 1 | 2 ]
(デフォルト値: 0)

This parameter defines how to handle ttypw passwords:
 0   only sysops and user with ttypw already set are allowed to change or delete
     TTYPW.
 1   as 0, and users who have logged in with password are also allowed to
     change their TTYPW.
