(SYSOP限定, init.bcm)
構文: USERL(IFE) [<days>]
(デフォルト値: 999)

Sets default lifetime for user mails. Sysops should define a value
corresponding to BBS harddisk space.
Value 0 makes no sense and leads automatically to a setting of 999.
999 is the max. value and means no deletion anyway.

例: USERLIFE 365

