\\WTEXT
(SYSOP限定)
構文: W(TEXT) <ファイル名>

Writes <filename> as textfile to disc. You can end upload with CTRL-Z.

例:
wt msg/ctext.dl                  to send a new connect textfile

Note: The used filename is every time seen from BCM home directory.
